{
  "stem": "11167.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 139.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And start to come a lot of people from Krakow, from Warsaw, who only can escape came to our part.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They thought that that will be a safe haven.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They will stay here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had one doctor, Dr.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Fischler.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He did stay with us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And where he disappeared, and what happened to him, I can't tell you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was a wonderful person-- a doctor, very nice person.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I think when he did smell out that it's going further-- it will not stay like that-- so he went away-- didn't say-- you see, you didn't even say to your mother where you going.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Everybody was terrified.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You're gone.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That is the-- that was in '39 through '41.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was earlier.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It-- he went away a few months before-- I remember a few good months before to-- from Poland-- from our home.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then in '41 started the big war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What happened?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sunday-- that was Shavuot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What you call this in--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Shavuot.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we came home, me and my brother, and my friends.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We came home joking and-- and--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From town.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went-- you know, we-- we went out for-- our town had a very big river, Ikva.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We used to go-- summer we used to go with, you know, with boats out-- everybody.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we came home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We went to sleep.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And 4 o'clock we heard bombs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Bombs is going.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Ambulances is running.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we didn't know what's going on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And 10 o'clock, Molotov-- that-- that is-- was our minister-- the Russians-- declared us war did start.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We mustn't be scared.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The Red Army will organize.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It is very sad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They're very sad, because in Kiev, they bombed not only this part where they took from-- from Poland, but they did bomb in Russia already.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Kiev was bombed.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
